name: Waterways
description:
ABOUT THE HOME ENERGY RATING SCALE
The HERS (Home Energy Rating System) Index allows buyers to compare the relative energy efficiency of different homes. The HERS Index home energy rating is determined by an independent RESNET-certified home energy rater ("Rater"). The lower a home’s score, the more energy efficient it is in comparison to the HERS referenced home. For every one-point decrease in the HERS Index score, there is a corresponding one percent (1%) reduction in energy consumption as compared to a home with a HERS Index of 100. A home with a HERS score of 100 reflects a home built to 2006 IEEC Building Codes. See the bottom of this page for more information on HERS scores.

amenities.name: Biking Pedestrian
amenities.description: Biking & Pedestrian Paths: Waterways is a connected community with multipurpose paths for walkers or bikers.

amenities.name: Grand Lagoon:
amenities.description: The Grand Lagoon: A private lagoon that is the ideal setting for an afternoon of kayaking or canoeing

amenities.name: Waterwags Dog
amenities.description: Waterwags Dog Park: with almost an acre of space there is plenty of room for your four-legged family members to run and play.

amenities.name: Center Waterways
amenities.description: The Center of Waterways life begins at the Marina Village. Beautiful marsh and saltwater views combined with dry slip storage, fresh water wet storage, retail shops and dining you can see why this is the heartbeat of Waterways

amenities.name: Waterways Marina
amenities.description: Waterways Marina gives boaters direct access to the Intracoastal Waterway.

amenities.name: Lakewood Pavilion
amenities.description: The Lakewood Pavilion provides immediate access to those looking to kayak or canoe on the Grand Lagoon, while also having a recreation space for community gatherings

amenities.name: gated entry
amenities.description: The gated entry with guard house makes a grand statement upon arrival to Waterways.  With a state of the art visitor management system residents can feel secure

amenities.name: Events Lawn
amenities.description: The Events Lawn in Ridgewood Park features a grass amphitheater, bocce ball, and plenty of space to play and relax

amenities.name: Throughout community
amenities.description: Throughout the community there are community gardens for residents to grow fresh veggies, herbs, and flowers

amenities.name: Bill Dance
amenities.description: Bill Dance Fishing Experience: The lakes are stocked with largemouth bass so you can experience first class fishing, right at home

amenities.name: Hawk Island
amenities.description: Hawk Island Nature Preserve located within the community is home to multiple species of birds, perfect for the avid bird watcher

amenities.name: Ridgewood Amenity
amenities.description: Ridgewood Amenity Center: Central to all of the neighborhoods within Waterways, it features a junior Olympic pool, fitness center, outdoor fireplace, and grill.
